{"about_the_game":"It is said that riches beyond imagination lay at the bottom of the dungeon of Faveg.<br>Driven by greed, adventurers flock there to meet their ends.<br>Will you be better than them?<br><br>Brave the hordes of monsters below as you train your party in this Roguelike take on class based progression.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198100/extras/30+_classes_size2.png?t=1727431237\" /><br>Every level up a decision, try to build competent fighters with semi-random class choices every level.<br>Certain class combinations will open up new growth paths for a character to take, try to find them all!<br>Will you build a wild berserker, a powerful wizard, a devout priest, or something in between?<br>Try out the first 8 levels on this demo!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198100/extras/LvlUp_Size.png?t=1727431237\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198100/extras/Skill_Sizes.png?t=1727431237\" /><br>Choose between hundreds of active and passive skills to grant your party an edge in battle!<br>Only 12 can be active at a time though, so think twice before swapping.<br>Will you carry powerful attacks, tide-turning buffs, or passives to improve your other skills?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198100/extras/Savagery_Size.PNG?t=1727431237\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198100/extras/Survive_Size.png?t=1727431237\" /><br>Experience the first 3 floors of the Dungeon of Faveg!<br>Every fight will pose a different challenge, can you overcome every single one, or will your strategy crumble?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198100/extras/Dead.gif